<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body style="font-family: sans-serif; max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 32px 16px; color: #1a1a1a;">
  <h2 style="font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 8px;">Hi <%= @first_name %>! 👋</h2>
  <p style="color: #555; margin-bottom: 16px;">
    You've been added to our <strong>Kids Min family portal</strong>.
    Complete your family profile to register your children for upcoming events and stay connected.
  </p>
  <p style="margin-bottom: 24px; color: #555;">
    This link expires in <strong>7 days</strong> and can only be used once.
  </p>
  <a href="<%= @invite_url %>"
     style="display:inline-block;background:#6d28d9;color:#fff;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:99px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;">
    Complete your profile →
  </a>
  <p style="margin-top: 28px; font-size: 13px; color: #888;">
    Or copy this link into your browser:<br>
    <span style="word-break:break-all;"><%= @invite_url %></span>
  </p>
  <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #aaa;">
    If you weren't expecting this email, you can safely ignore it.
  </p>
</body>
</html>
